{"itemid":298,"subject":"Time Is Running Out","event":"Time is running out to nominate for this year's Hugo Awards.  Nominations close on February 28, remember.  Members of Denvention III (last year's worldcon) and/ or Anticipation (this year's Montreal worldcon) can nominate on line at:\r\n\r\nhttp://www.anticipationsf.ca/pub/hugos/nominations.php\r\n\r\nIf you're not a member of either worldcon, you can't nominate.  However, it is easy enough to sign up for Anticipation, as either an attending or supporting member.  Just go to:\r\n\r\nhttp://www.anticipationsf.ca/pub/members/membership.php\r\n\r\nNominate now... or you can't complain when the shortlist is announced and your own favorites aren't on it.  \r\n\r\n(For MY favorites and recommendations, see the series of posts I made last week).\r\n\r\nTime is also running out for my sale on signed copies of WINDHAVEN.  If you would like to snag a WINDHAVEN hardcover for $18, book rate shipping included, act now.  On March 1, the price goes up to $26.","ditemid":76458,"eventtime":"2009-02-25 11:29:00","props":{"personifi_word_count":163,"opt_screening":"F","commentalter":1235620559},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2009-02-25 18:39:21","anum":170,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/76458.html","event_timestamp":1235561340,"reply_count":7,"comments":[{"collapsed":0,"shown":1,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/34996430/1395886","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/76458.html?replyto=5540266","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/76458.html?thread=5540266#t5540266","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/76458.html?thread=5540266#t5540266","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/76458.html?thread=5540266#t5540266","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"shsilver","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://shsilver.livejournal.com/","sta