 track this one down and get you an answer right away.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","ctime":"February 26 2009, 01:03:46 UTC","parent":5541802,"massactions":0,"subject":"Re: Ordering","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://assistantty.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"assistantty","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"assistantty","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://assistantty.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"assistantty","ctime_ts":1235610226,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/76458.html?replyto=5542314","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/76458.html?thread=5542314#t5542314","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/76458.html?thread=5542314#t5542314","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/76458.html?thread=5542314#t5542314","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"mafanaut","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://mafanaut.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5542314,"talkid":21649,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/76458.html?thread=5542314#t5542314","above":5542058,"upictitle":"mafanaut: pic#0","article":"Thanks a lot! (Especially for the fast answer, wow!) As I said, it's ok for me to wait for it and that George gets spammed in both positive and negative ways is clear to me.<br /><br />That's why I waited a month for my second mail and I'll happily wait a few days or weeks longer, as long as I know that work is in progress. :-)<br /><br />It's 02.10 a.m. here in Austria, so for now I wish you a pleasant day (or whatever it is 